titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: WOMEN LYMPH NODES PATHOLOGY RESULT NEGATIVE TOTAL - Description

div.p: WOMEN LYMPH NODES PATHOLOGY RESULT NEGATIVE TOTAL is the total number of women who had a pathology examination with a negative result (CYTOLOGY RESULT CODE recorded as National Code 'C2' or NEEDLE CORE BIOPSY RESULT CODE FOR AXILLARY LYMPH NODE recorded as Code 'LB2').
